data.description: Do not miss out on this nicely updated Raised Ranch home with a total of that has 1,826 total living space.  4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths home with an eat in kitchen.  Roof and siding on the house and garage 2 years old.  The deck is newer and there is a fenced in yard with a 2 car garage.  Hot water heater is new this year.  The basement bath has been newly updated.  Interior of the home has been newly painted.  Master bedroom has walk in bathroom with a whirlpool tub.  This home is looking for a new owner.  Do not miss out on this one
